rows.label: tlk45200111_03_msg0002
rows.name: You're friends with so many Blades!

rows.label: tlk45200111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I heard something super interesting
when me and my mum went along
to Harapekko Canteen...

rows.label: tlk45200111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
There's a very bad person somewhere
around here. I think they called him
a "cork wristel hunter"?

rows.label: tlk45200111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I was kinda far away, so I couldn't
hear so well.

rows.label: tlk45200111_03_msg0006
rows.name:
I dunno the details exactly, but it
sounds pretty exciting! You should go
to Harapekko Canteen and find out!
